			"content": "<span> </span><h3 id=\"b3_9\"><a class=\"crossref\" id=\"26290\"></a>Behandling</h3><p>Terapirekommendationerna <a href=\"#86925\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-mini pageLink\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-right fa-white\"></i></a>.</p><div class=\"clearfix\"></div>",
